svg.title: Countries of Europe
svg.desc: A blank Map of Europe. Every country has an id which is its ISO-3116-1-ALPHA2 code in lower case. Members of the EU have a class="eu", countries in europe (which I found turkey to be but russia not) have a class="europe". Image based on a map (http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Image:Europe_countries.svg) by JÃºlio "Tintazul" Reis. made by Marian "maix" Sigler.
